title: Paul's Boutique
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Pleasant/fun burger place opened 2014 not far from the historical center of the city. Menu offers around 8 veggie and vegan dishes. Vegans can get information about the ingredients of the the burgers in the pamphlets on the counter.
